title: Khun Samee Karmalor Tee Rak
overview: Pimpha is a beautiful, confident, fashionable woman but was deeply hurt. A pregnant woman suddenly appeared on Pimpha's wedding day claiming that the groom was her husband. Because of this nightmare Pimpha ended at a club drunk. The next morning came another shocked to Pimpha as she woke up laying in bed with a stranger. Ridchawee was angered because Pimpha claiming not to remember anything about last night. How will this entaglement conclude...
